Open Congress is sponsored by the Sunlight Foundation. The Sunlight Foundation is a unique foundation whose values lay in creating a route to political reform through the funding of technological software tools. The Sunlight Foundation has partnered with the Participatory Politics Foundation over the past months to build Open Congress in a move that is notable and grand. The Participatory Politics Foundation builds software tools to maximize the effectiveness of efforts at political change on the internet. We are seeking to build more software tools to build a meritocratic, creative, participatory political system we can all call our own.
